TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: SELECT Reference.Reference_sub_key_1 as Reference_sub_key_1, Reference.Desc_1 as Desc_1, Reference.Desc_2 as Desc_2, Reference.Reference_key as Reference_key, Reference.Reference_sub_key_2 as Reference_sub_key_2 FROM Reference with (nolock)

TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Post SQL
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE:
update gross_margin_style_account g set py_dollars =dollars ,py_adj_extended_cost_dollars = adj_extended_cost_dollars where g.fiscal_year=2009 and g.fiscal_Period<5 and g.gross_margin_ind='Y' and g.slba_division_code in ('CW','CH') ; commit;
update ( select g.py_dollars, g.py_adj_extended_cost_dollars, case when invoiced_quality_code ='1' or invoiced_quality_code ='6' and upper(nvl(sm.level_1_name,'')) != 'FINANCE' then decode(g.sales_measure_name,'Gross OS', decode(sign(nvl(avg_price_dollars,0)),0,dollars,g.garments*avg_price_dollars),dollars) else dollars end recast_dollars, case when invoiced_quality_code ='1' or invoiced_quality_code ='6' and upper(nvl(sm.level_1_name,'')) != 'FINANCE' then decode(cost_measure_name,'OS COGS', decode(sign(nvl(avg_cost_dollars,0)),0,adj_extended_cost_dollars,g.garments*avg_cost_dollars),adj_extended_cost_dollars) else adj_extended_cost_dollars end recast_cost from slba.gross_margin_style_account g left outer join slba.Average_Cost_Price_by_style a on a.style_num=g.style_num and a.division_group=g.division_group and a.company_code=g.company_code and a.fiscal_year= g.fiscal_year and a.fiscal_period = g.fiscal_period left outer join slba.style_master_1 sm on sm.style_num = g.style_num and sm.division_group = g.division_group and sm.company_code=g.company_code where g.fiscal_year=2009 and g.fiscal_Period<5 and g.gross_margin_ind='Y' and g.slba_division_code in ('CW','CH') and sm.division_group in ('slsp') ) set py_dollars =recast_dollars ,py_adj_extended_cost_dollars = recast_cost ; commit;

V_GM.GROSS_MARGIN_IND, V_GM.INVOICED_QUALITY_CODE, V_GM.SAP_PROFIT_CENTER_NUM, V_GM.SAP_SOLDTO_CUST, V_GM.PY_ADJ_EXTENDED_COST_DOLLARS, V_GM.PY_DOLLARS,V_GM.ITEM_ID, V_GM.SOURCE_ORDER_TYPE, V_GM.dollars_local_currency, V_GM.adj_ext_cst_dol_local_currency, V_GM.gl_currency_code, V_GM.SALES_ORG,V_GM.FINADJ_MEASURE_TYPE as FINADJ_MEASURE_TYPE,V_GM.sap_shipto_cust, V_GM.Sales_Deal, SOURCE_ACCOUNT_NUM , H.SALES_MEASURE_NAME AS SALES_MEASURE_NAME , H.COST_MEASURE_NAME AS COST_MEASURE_NAME , I.REPRESENTATIVE_STYLE_NUM AS REPRESENTATIVE_STYLE_NUM , H.FISCAL_YEAR AS FISCAL_YEAR , H.FISCAL_PERIOD AS FISCAL_PERIOD , H.FISCAL_WEEK AS FISCAL_WEEK , H.SALES_CATEGORY AS SALES_CATEGORY , H.TRANSACTION_CATEGORY AS TRANSACTION_CATEGORY , H.CORE_IND AS CORE_IND , H.DISTRIBUTION_CTR_FACILITY_ID AS DISTRIBUTION_CTR_FACILITY_ID , H.DOZENS AS DOZENS , H.UNITS AS UNITS , H.GARMENTS AS GARMENTS , H.DOLLARS AS DOLLARS , H.ADJ_EXTENDED_COST_DOLLARS AS UPD_USER , SYSDATE AS UPD_DATE , H.SAP_PROFIT_CENTER_NUM AS SAP_PROFIT_CENTER_NUM , H.SAP_SOLDTO_CUST AS SAP_SOLDTO_CUST , H.PY_ADJ_EXTENDED_COST_DOLLARS AS PY_ADJ_EXTENDED_COST_DOLLARS , H.PY_DOLLARS AS PY_DOLLARS , H.ITEM_ID AS ITEM_ID, --PPM#87017 LCA CHANGE H.SOURCE_ORDER_TYPE AS SOURCE_ORDER_TYPE, --PPM#87017 LCA CHANGE H.DOLLARS_LOCAL_CURRENCY AS DOLLARS_LOCAL_CURRENCY, H.ADJ_EXT_CST_DOL_LOCAL_CURRENCY AS ADJ_EXT_CST_DOL_LOCAL_CURRENCY, H.GL_CURRENCY_CODE AS GL_CURRENCY_CODE ,H.SALES_ORG AS SALES_ORG,H.FINADJ_MEASURE_TYPE as FINADJ_MEASURE_TYPE,H.sap_shipto_cust as
